tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I went to Diento during the COVID pandemic and was impressed as soon as I walked in with all the safety precautions. I was given a mask, gloves, hair net and an apron upon entry. The entire staff was in PPE suits and face shields. The room looked extremely sterile and clean. All sanitization protocols were followed. 
Dr Chheda was extremely professional and explained my condition to me. Seeing my apprehension on getting my wisdom tooth removed he calmed me down and assured me it would be a short and painless procedure , and yes , it was!! 
I feel absolutely fine after surgery and would definitely go back to Diento again! 
I strongly recommend this clinic as extremely safe, professional and fabulous. Thanks DIENTO :)
reply_text: Thank you for the kind words.
